o me, his dark eyes combing my every move. 'Do you always hold your guitar like that?'I dropped my pick. 'Do you always shop at Hot Topic?\n\n- Tara Kelly, Amplified\n|\nWe have nothing to lose, nothing to gain, nothing we desired anymore- except to make our lives into a work of art.\n\n- Lana"